item.title: Spectral Clustering SNS Target Data
item.description: The spallation neutron source (SNS) is a consumable component which wears out due to radiation damage and cavitation erosion. We propose a spectral clustering based method to detect damage in the target.

item.title: Image Processing and Optimization
item.description: Using weighted convex minimization to solve the image inpainting and de-noising problems.
